track.name: Moon Dreams
comments: Strange and warm and dreamy and cool.
Tonight is the biggest moon of the year!!! Cinco de Mayo 2012!!!Whoooohooooo!
I am still not a miles davis fan.
walking with you on the moon...in a dream...
só pra sair um pouco daqui
Definitely different than the rest of the album, I agree. Love it all the same though!
Maybe it's just me, but this track felt like the odd one out on BotC (not saying that in a bad way, but it just had a completely different feel to it, much closer to his later sound).

last few days of my senior year just before exams I sat as one of two people in math class and it was just drizzling outside all day... sat in class listening to this on repeat for a good half hour before moving on to the rest of the album. I even ended up flat out skipping that exam for paganfest that day; I tried to go early to find the teachers for the exams I still had but they were nowhere to be found... they just exempted me anyway even though I didn't have the grades (well maybe I did) and certainly not the attendance record for it. hah :)
something very special, even for Miles...
